STATE
v.
Joseph Marion HEAD. No. 629P04-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 20th day of April 2005 by Defendant for the Relief asked for and demanded within the state and federal prison and court records and etc. records relating thereto based on the asserted within said records:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 4th day of May 2005."
